Опис вакансії
BDO Centers LLC, is a representative Subsidiary of BDO Group headquartered in Brussels, Belgium:
80,000 people employed
$9 billion revenue generates
160 countries present
For our new office in Kyiv we are looking for amazing young talents, that want to be part of an internationally well known organization with an excellent reputation and a legacy of 100 years in the business. We are already a great team of more than 60 employees in Kyiv, but we want to expand our business operations further. If you have the feeling you are ready for your next career step — and you are not shy to enter the world of Strategy Consulting — then this is your chance.Not we are looking for a prominent Analyst\Rerearch specialist, who will be reponsible for data collection and analysis for our foreign projects, bringing analyticak expertize onboard.The scope of your main duties will include the following functions and tasks:1) Conducting research and analysis projects in service of clients,2) Lead the projects targeted for on-demand analyses of:• market shares,• competitive environment,• business strategies,• business trends,• financial analysis,3) Formulating and testing hypotheses, and developing and communicating findings4) Developing strategic frameworks, conducting design of business processes in a request of clients5) Assessing the pros and cons of possible strategies6) Responsibility for problem-solving in a primarily English-speaking7) Preparation of Point of Views, Go-to-Market Strategies, Company Profiles, Business Studies8) Conducting an analysis of the companies via financial modeling, investment analysis, business processes analysis and desk research9) Help design and implement large-scale organisational change programs10) Work under processes optimization (generate sample research templates)Our successful candidate has:
Good analytical skills,
Business-oriented,
Basic understanding of business running,
Basic understanding of economy models,
Financial literacy.
Upper intermediate or advanced coloqual and business English.
Quick learner, ability and desire to study,
Autonomy in work,
Work clarity and accuracy,
High level of responsibility,
Ability to multitask,
The comapy offers:— Competitive salary, paid in Euro (to be discussed following your skills level),— Toal transperancy and Labour Law adherence,— English and German classes,— Very friend;ly and positive enviromnet,— Team building events, possibilities to study and grow your professional grade.Once you are young and passionate about the role — don’t hesitate to contact us right now.Learn more about us:www.bdo.dehttps://www.linkedin.com/company/bdo-centers/
